snippet.title: Operation Amber Sky - THE DEVIL WE WANT in Ghost Recon: Breakpoint | Extreme Difficulty
snippet.description:
PS4 Gameplay.
➡Mission from the live event Operation Amber Sky. The reward for completing this mission is blueprint for the G2. Assault. Highest rate of fire in class.
Extreme difficulty. Pathfinder class. Using L115A3 & 4-AC.
Location: Chem-Extraction Complex, Mount Hodgson.
Thank you for watching and subscribing!
👍🔔
